        </span>` : ''}
        ${p.isPrime ? `<span class="badge badge-prime" title="Amazon Prime">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="12" height="12"><path d="M3 8l9-5 9 5v8l-9 5-9-5V8z"/><path d="M12 22V12"/><path d="M3 8l9 4 9-4"/></svg>
          Prime
